{
  "text": "in mice hippocampus as a result of aging [CITATION_1] and is downregulated in early AD as well [CITATION_2] . A significant loss of the C␣, B55␥, and PR61 subunit mRNA in the AD hippocampus has been described [CITATION_3] . Although together these findings point to a likely deregulation of PP2A in AD, it is not known whether the protein expression levels or distribution of a specific PP2A holoenzyme are altered in AD.",
  "correct_citation": {
